  m_Name: SagawaKaito
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Sagawa Kaito
  description: 'A young man with the one and only goal to care for the family that
    his mother and father had worked so hard to build. He studies long hours to maintain
    his good grades with a part-time job on the side to alleviate his single mother''s
    financial burdens. He''s not someone that likes to spend time messing around,
    nor does he want anyone else''s pity, no matter how much sleep he loses. He needs
    to stay focused to keep anything from falling apart. Unfortunately, after getting
    thrown into a pair project assigned by Yuri-sensei, one girl would become his
    biggest distraction: Takasu Haruko.'
  fullBody: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a4a514bdec7a297448e94153fd438c5b, type: 3}
